fields.name: Samsug S23
fields.description:
The Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra brings predictably minor upgrades - camera tweaks here and new chipset there, mostly - but how much can you really improve on the S22 Ultra in just a year? We'll attempt to answer that question and see if the new Ultra can spark excitement in ways the specsheet couldn't.

And it's an expansive specsheet, of course. At the Ultra's heart is the Snapdragon 8 Gen 2, and it's one specifically made for the Galaxies - with higher clock rates than competitors get. The latest Qualcomm top-end chip also comes with efficiency promises, and we would never say no to some extra endurance.

The camera sees the introduction of a new 200MP sensor, up from the 108MP resolution of Ultras past. The couple of telephotos remain a staple of the lineup and a standout feature in the market where 10x optical zoom is nowhere to be found outside of the Samsung offerings. The 2023 Ultra is still the only model in the lineup with an autofocusing ultrawide - more of an ongoing rant we just had to include here about the lack of it on the lesser S23s than an actual noteworthy feature of the ultimate Galaxy.

fields.name: Royal 58 Inches 4K UHD Smart TV
fields.description:
The Royal 58″ UHD Smart Signature TV RTV58SG7N/B is a feature-packed television that brings a world of entertainment to your fingertips. With its sleek design and vibrant display, this Ultra High Definition Television is sure to enhance your viewing experience.
Firstly, the Royal 58-inch smart TV RTV58SG7N/B delivers crisp and clear visuals, ensuring a delightful viewing experience. Whether you’re watching movies, sports, or playing video games, the picture quality is immersive and engaging.
Secondly, Equipped with multiple connectivity options, this smart TV offers versatility in connecting various devices. It features HDMI ports, USB ports, and AV inputs, allowing you to connect gaming consoles, set-top boxes, media players, and more.
Thirdly, Royal 58-inch Smart Television also comes with built-in Wi-Fi, making it convenient to connect to your home network and access online content wirelessly. In conclusion, the Royal 58-inch smart TV RTV58SG7N/B offers an impressive range of features and functionality. With its smart capabilities, stunning display, and versatile connectivity options, it provides an immersive and enjoyable viewing experience for all your entertainment needs.

fields.name: Patek Phillppe
fields.description:
In this chapter, you learned how to define canonical URLs for models. You created SEO-friendly URLs
for blog posts, and you implemented object pagination for your post list. You also learned how to work
with Django forms and model forms. You created a system to recommend posts by email and created
a comment system for your blog.
In the next chapter, you will create a tagging system for the blog. You will learn how to build complex
QuerySets to retrieve objects by similarity. You will learn how to create custom template tags and
filters. You will also build a custom sitemap and feed for your blog posts and implement a full-text
search functionality for your posts.

fields.name: Shopping Cart
fields.description:
Stripe can push real-time events to our application by using webhooks. A webhook, also called a callback, can be thought of as an event-driven API instead of a request-driven API. Instead of polling the
Stripe API frequently to know when a new payment is completed, Stripe can send an HTTP request to a
URL of our application to notify of successful payments in real time. These notification of these events
will be asynchronous, when the event occurs, regardless of our synchronous calls to the Stripe API.
We will build a webhook endpoint to receive Stripe events. The webhook will consist of a view that will
receive a JSON payload with the event information to process it. We will use the event information to
mark orders as paid when the checkout session is successfully completed.

fields.name: Gionee M15, 6.67″ (8GB RAM, 128GB ROM) Android 11
fields.description:
Gionee M15 Summary
 

Gionee M15 smartphone was launched in May 2021. The phone comes with a 6.67-inch touchscreen display with a resolution of 1080×2400 pixels and an aspect ratio of 20:9.Gionee M15 comes with 8GB of RAM. The Gionee M15 runs Android and is powered by a 5100mAh battery. The Gionee M15 supports proprietary fast charging.

As far as the cameras are concerned, the Gionee M15 on the rear packs a 48-megapixel primary camera with an f/1.7 aperture; a 5-megapixel camera with an f/2.2 aperture; a 2-megapixel camera with an f/2.4 aperture, and a 2-megapixel camera with an f/2.4 aperture. The rear camera setup has autofocus. It sports a 16-megapixel camera on the front for selfies.

Gionee M15 is based on Android and packs 128GB of inbuilt storage.

Connectivity options on the Gionee M15 include Wi-Fi. Sensors on the phone include accelerometer, proximity sensor, and fingerprint sensor.
